<p>Components are reusable parts of the user interface that have been made to support a variety of applications. Any components with interactive capabilities can also be navigated using the keyboard, for accessibility purposes.</p>
<p>Each component in the gov.cy Unified Design System has guidance on its use and coded examples. If you are using the our <a href="../getting-started/developer-assets">developers assets</a> and the code in our documentation, coded examples will render the same as in the Design System.</p>
<p>You can use individual components in many different <a href="../patterns">patterns</a> and contexts.</p>
<p>Use the links on this page to navigated to the desired component.</p>

